OL,3,CFortnightly bin collections to be
OL,4,Crolled out despite strike action
OL,6,FFortnightly bin collections in
OL,7,FBirmingham will begin in June 2026,
OL,8,Feven if bin workers are still on
OL,9,Fstrike, according to the city council.
OL,11,F20,000 households per fortnight will
OL,12,Fbegin to have their regular and
OL,13,Frecycling waste collected on
OL,14,Falternative weeks.
OL,16,FThe authority said the "transformed"
OL,17,Fservice will also include weekly food
OL,18,Fwaste collections.
