OL,3,CFortnightly bin collections to be
OL,4,Crolled out despite strike action
OL,6,FThe plans, which are subject to
OL,7,Fcabinet approval, are expected to see
OL,8,Frecycling rates double from the 22%
OL,9,Fachieved before the current industrial
OL,10,Faction.
OL,12,FHowever, this comes a day after agency
OL,13,Fworkers joined striking bin workers on
OL,14,Fpicket lines in the city centre over
OL,15,Fclaims of "bullying and harassment at
OL,16,Fthe council's refuse department two
OL,17,Fweeks ago."
