OL,3,CFortnightly bin collections to be
OL,4,Crolled out despite strike action
OL,6,FAround 200 picketers were at a rally
OL,7,Fheld by Unite The Union at Smithfield
OL,8,FDepot on Pershore Street in Birmingham
OL,9,Fon 1 December, to mark the first day
OL,10,Fof strike action by agency refuse
OL,11,Fworkers.
OL,13,FUnite said the Job & Talent agency
OL,14,Fworkers had voted in favour of strike
OL,15,Faction to join the picket along with
OL,16,Fbin workers from Birmingham city
OL,17,Fcouncil.
