OL,3,CFortnightly bin collections to be
OL,4,Crolled out despite strike action
OL,6,FBirmingham City Council has described
OL,7,Fthe bullying claims as "unfounded" and
OL,8,Fsays an investigation found that no
OL,9,F"blacklisting" had occurred.
OL,11,FThe council had posted on social media
OL,12,Fto say it had decided to suspend all
OL,13,Frefuse collection services.
OL,15,FHowever, the collections have now
OL,16,Fresumed but the council admitted
OL,17,F"historically the service has not been
OL,18,Fgood enough, with a high level of
OL,19,Fmissed collections and one of the
OL,20,Flowest recycling rates in the country".
