OL,3,CFortnightly bin collections to be
OL,4,Crolled out despite strike action
OL,6,FThey added that "this must change".
OL,8,FThe council says despite the ongoing
OL,9,Findustrial action, the contingency
OL,10,Fplan is working and productivity has
OL,11,Fimproved.
OL,13,FThey went on to say that there has
OL,14,Fbeen a 52% improvement rate on missed
OL,15,Fcollections and a 22% improvement on
OL,16,Ftonnage collected per employee.
