OL,3,CFortnightly bin collections to be
OL,4,Crolled out despite strike action
OL,6,FIn addition to improved productivity,
OL,7,Fthe council said new arrangements are
OL,8,Fin place to monitor the quality of
OL,9,Fservices as well as training for staff
OL,10,Fand managers.
OL,12,FBirmingham City Council, Cllr Majid
OL,13,FMahmood said: "Residents will see a
OL,14,Freal difference with the new services.
OL,16,F"We have already made some changes,
OL,17,Fwith our new council-owned fleet fully
OL,18,Foperational - there is less reliance
OL,19,Fon hired vehicles, improved
OL,20,Freliability and better consistency in
OL,21,Fcollections.
