OL,3,CFortnightly bin collections to be
OL,4,Crolled out despite strike action
OL,6,F"Our crews have the tools they need to
OL,7,Fdeliver a more reliable, efficient
OL,8,Fservice while also supporting the
OL,9,Fcity's environmental goals, benefiting
OL,10,Fboth residents and staff.
OL,12,F"The transformed service will bring
OL,13,FBirmingham into line with other
OL,14,Fcouncils, improve recycling rates and
OL,15,Fprovide a service our residents need
OL,16,Fand deserve."
OL,18,FThe report will go to cabinet on 9
OL,19,FDecember.
